doc.after: Shoshone National Forest is managed by the U S Forest Service an agency within the U S Department of Agriculture The forest is separated into five districts and from 2008 and 2012 had an average staff of 165 employees and an annual operating budget of 17 500 000 26 The headquarters and a visitor center are in Cody Wyoming and a smaller information center is in Lander Wyoming There are local ranger district offices in Cody Dubois and Lander 27
